individuals who have completed a bs or two year ms program in the us or other english speaking country are not required to submit toefl scores previously admitted students who wish to change their degree objective from ms to ph d must petition the ges admissions committee for more information please see our graduate admission page department of geological & environmental sciences 450 serra mall bldg 320 stanford ca 94305 2115 650 723 0847 terms of use copyright complaints related resources hartley conference center health and safety computers resources room resources how can we help maps & directions stanfordwho office of the registrar contact us connect to earth sciences facebook itunes u twitter youtube
